Sentencas: Liquid/solid reaction couples were used to investigate the interface reactions between steel interconnect materials, such as Ni and 430 stainless steel (430SS).
Titulo: Interfacial reactions between Ni/430 stainless steel as the interconnect material and Ag-Cu alloy fillers in a solid oxide fuel cell system

Sentencas: and Ag-Cu alloys used as fillers in a solid oxide fuel cell system.
Titulo: Interfacial reactions between Ni/430 stainless steel as the interconnect material and Ag-Cu alloy fillers in a solid oxide fuel cell system

Sentencas: The Cu atoms diffused into the Ni side, forming a (Cu, Ni) solid solution at the Ag-Cu/Ni interface.
Titulo: Interfacial reactions between Ni/430 stainless steel as the interconnect material and Ag-Cu alloy fillers in a solid oxide fuel cell system

Sentencas: The (Cu. Ni) solid solution acts a diffuse barrier that prevents the diffusion of Cu atoms into the Ni side.
Titulo: Interfacial reactions between Ni/430 stainless steel as the interconnect material and Ag-Cu alloy fillers in a solid oxide fuel cell system

Sentencas: In the Ag-Cu/electroplating Ni/430SS couple, the reaction layer is the gamma-(Fe, Ni) phase and the interface is smooth when the Cu content is less than 20 at.% in Ag-Cu alloys.
Titulo: Interfacial reactions between Ni/430 stainless steel as the interconnect material and Ag-Cu alloy fillers in a solid oxide fuel cell system

Sentencas: As the Cu content increases over 20 at.%, the interface morphology becomes rougher and the reaction layers are (Cu, Ni)+ gamma-(Fe, Ni) phases.
Titulo: Interfacial reactions between Ni/430 stainless steel as the interconnect material and Ag-Cu alloy fillers in a solid oxide fuel cell system
